# i18n

- All user-visible strings via translation keys (`labelKey`, `titleKey`, `| translate`).
- Add every new key to **both** `public/assets/en.json` and `public/assets/bh.json` (single file per language).
- In TS, return key strings for labels (e.g. `statusLabel()` ‚Üí `'portal.employee.features.shipments.table.status.${status}'`).
- Do not embed English prose in templates when a key exists or should exist.

## Key tree (mirrors `src/app/` layers)

```
shared.*                          ‚Äî shell chrome + form/table/confirm frameworks
guest.*                           ‚Äî public pages (landing, sign-in, login, register)
portal.shell.{admin|employee}.*   ‚Äî portal badge in sidebar brand
portal.admin.nav.*                ‚Äî admin sidebar
portal.admin.pages.*              ‚Äî admin route titleKey
portal.admin.features.<feature>.* ‚Äî admin feature (form, table)
portal.employee.nav.*             ‚Äî employee sidebar
portal.employee.pages.*           ‚Äî employee route titleKey
portal.employee.features.<domain>.<feature>.* ‚Äî employee feature (form, table)
```

### Shared (`shared.*`)

| Path | Use for |
|------|---------|
| `shared.sidebar.*` | Portal sidebar chrome |
| `shared.topbar.*` | Portal + shared topbar widgets (theme, language, account) |
| `shared.form.common.*` | Form footer (previous/next/submit), stepper meta (`stepOf`, `percentComplete`, `stepLocked`), field errors |
| `shared.table.common.*` | Table loading, empty, pagination, row actions |
| `shared.confirm.common.*` | Confirmation dialog cancel/confirm button labels (defaults; do not duplicate per feature) |

### Guest (`guest.*`)

| Path | Use for |
|------|---------|
| `guest.landing.*` | Landing page |
| `guest.signIn.*` | Portal picker |
| `guest.login.*` | Employee + admin login pages |
| `guest.register.*` | Company registration page chrome |
| `guest.register.form.*` | Register company stepper form |
| `guest.topbar.*`, `guest.footer.*` | Guest shell |

